{"tid":1925081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疫苗出左後，炒價你肯用幾多錢打？","createTime":"2020-03-14T06:24:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T07:23:47.000Z","uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"af459a987c0dba52536a98c512b7905152d49858","tid":1925081,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T06:24:33.000Z","msg":"如果真係人工病毒依招真係奇招，七傷拳黎<br />\n雖然中國好傷 但中共唔介意70%人受感染 變黑肺 最緊要90%人好返後去工廠繼續開工就得 生活必需品都要依靠中國既低階工業<br />\n但民主國家醫療開支貴好多 經濟一衰退 就好易比人乘虛而入 <br />\n而家個勢沒完沒了 超越sars 成功變種步入穩定期<br />\n都唔會指望病毒自己變返弱 而家唯一依靠係疫苗<br />\n<br />\n如果而家有你比幾錢打？<br />\n如果已經10%香港人感染左，又肯比幾錢？"},{"pid":"dc33e0847f5068407b47a098960d4bb67f7a8758","tid":1925081,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T06:28:17.000Z","msg":"疫苗要醫生打,馬馬地好炒"},{"pid":"b9a76babcda5ca2465c1e28e811df6c27444a715","tid":1925081,"uid":232250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T06:31:38.000Z","msg":"純粹鳩估。打左都冇用。<br />\n經過咁多人種感染過，唔多唔少都變左種。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f38a7bc2b3ca08a70cd91ffee4b8df97780796","tid":1925081,"uid":63779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9a76babcda5ca2465c1e28e811df6c27444a715","tid":1925081,"uid":232250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T06:31:38.000Z","msg":"純粹鳩估。打左都冇用。<br />\n經過咁多人種感染過，唔多唔少都變左種。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:06:56.000Z","msg":"病毒正常係愈多人中傳愈多代就會變得愈廢。"},{"pid":"5d0117a81ca0e001bcd576374f8a91c0a5c29e33","tid":1925081,"uid":279606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:08:37.000Z","msg":"免費"},{"pid":"d92912ebcec92992489b59b16349f3c0f8060a1b","tid":1925081,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:09:56.000Z","msg":"窮人唔打咪一樣仆街"},{"pid":"60bba08ec8a0a936e555bbccbde36be5bf9143f7","tid":1925081,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quot